#. <section class="sutta" id="an8.9"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "an8.9:0.1"
msgid "Aṅguttara Nikāya 8"
msgstr "Numbered Discourses 8"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "an8.9:0.2"
msgid "1. Mettāvagga"
msgstr "1. Love"

#. </p><h1>
msgctxt "an8.9:0.3"
msgid "9. Nandasutta"
msgstr "9. Nanda"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pli" id="pts-vp-pli4.167"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc1"></a>
msgctxt "an8.9:1.1"
msgid "“‘kulaputto’ti, bhikkhave, nandaṃ sammā vadamāno vadeyya."
msgstr "“Mendicants, you could rightly call Nanda ‘son of a good family’,"

msgctxt "an8.9:1.2"
msgid "‘Balavā’ti, bhikkhave, nandaṃ sammā vadamāno vadeyya."
msgstr "‘strong’,"

msgctxt "an8.9:1.3"
msgid "‘Pāsādiko’ti, bhikkhave, nandaṃ sammā vadamāno vadeyya."
msgstr "‘lovely’,"

msgctxt "an8.9:1.4"
msgid "‘Tibbarāgo’ti, bhikkhave, nandaṃ sammā vadamāno vadeyya."
msgstr "and ‘lustful’."

#. VAR: yehi → yena (pts1, mr)
msgctxt "an8.9:1.5"
msgid ""
"Kimaññatra, bhikkhave, nando indriyesu guttadvāro, bhojane mattaññū, "
"jāgariyaṃ anuyutto, satisampajaññena samannāgato, yehi nando sakkoti "
"paripuṇṇaṃ parisuddhaṃ brahmacariyaṃ carituṃ."
msgstr ""
"How could he live the full and pure spiritual life unless he guards the "
"sense doors, eats in moderation, is dedicated to wakefulness, and has "
"mindfulness and situational awareness?"

msgctxt "an8.9:1.6"
msgid "Tatridaṃ, bhikkhave, nandassa indriyesu guttadvāratāya hoti."
msgstr "This is how Nanda guards the sense doors."

msgctxt "an8.9:1.7"
msgid ""
"Sace, bhikkhave, nandassa puratthimā disā āloketabbā hoti, sabbaṃ cetasā "
"samannāharitvā nando puratthimaṃ disaṃ āloketi:"
msgstr ""
"If he has to look to the east, he wholeheartedly concentrates before "
"looking, thinking:"

msgctxt "an8.9:1.8"
msgid ""
"‘evaṃ me puratthimaṃ disaṃ ālokayato nābhijjhādomanassā pāpakā akusalā "
"dhammā anvāssavissantī’ti."
msgstr ""
"‘When I look to the east, bad, unskillful qualities of desire and aversion "
"will not overwhelm me.’"

msgctxt "an8.9:1.9"
msgid "Itiha tattha sampajāno hoti."
msgstr "In this way he’s aware of the situation."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc2"></a>
msgctxt "an8.9:2.1"
msgid "Sace, bhikkhave, nandassa pacchimā disā āloketabbā hoti … pe …"
msgstr "If he has to look to the west …"

msgctxt "an8.9:2.2"
msgid "uttarā disā āloketabbā hoti …"
msgstr "north …"

msgctxt "an8.9:2.3"
msgid "dakkhiṇā disā āloketabbā hoti …"
msgstr "south …"

msgctxt "an8.9:2.4"
msgid "uddhaṃ ulloketabbā hoti …"
msgstr "up …"

msgctxt "an8.9:2.5"
msgid "adho oloketabbā hoti …"
msgstr "down …"

msgctxt "an8.9:2.6"
msgid ""
"anudisā anuviloketabbā hoti, sabbaṃ cetasā samannāharitvā nando anudisaṃ "
"anuviloketi:"
msgstr ""
"If he has to survey the intermediate directions, he wholeheartedly "
"concentrates before looking, thinking:"

msgctxt "an8.9:2.7"
msgid ""
"‘evaṃ me anudisaṃ anuvilokayato nābhijjhādomanassā pāpakā akusalā dhammā "
"anvāssavissantī’ti."
msgstr ""
"‘When I survey the intermediate directions, bad, unskillful qualities of "
"desire and aversion will not overwhelm me.’"

msgctxt "an8.9:2.8"
msgid "Itiha tattha sampajāno hoti."
msgstr "In this way he’s aware of the situation."

msgctxt "an8.9:2.9"
msgid "Idaṃ kho, bhikkhave, nandassa indriyesu guttadvāratāya hoti."
msgstr "This is how Nanda guards the sense doors."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc3"></a>
msgctxt "an8.9:3.1"
msgid "Tatridaṃ, bhikkhave, nandassa bhojane mattaññutāya hoti."
msgstr "This is how Nanda eats in moderation."

msgctxt "an8.9:3.2"
msgid "Idha, bhikkhave, nando paṭisaṅkhā yoniso āhāraṃ āhāreti:"
msgstr "Nanda reflects properly on the food he eats:"

msgctxt "an8.9:3.3"
msgid ""
"‘neva davāya na madāya na maṇḍanāya na vibhūsanāya, yāvadeva imassa kāyassa "
"ṭhitiyā yāpanāya vihiṃsūparatiyā brahmacariyānuggahāya iti purāṇañca vedanaṃ "
"paṭihaṅkhāmi, navañca vedanaṃ na uppādessāmi, yātrā ca me bhavissati "
"anavajjatā ca phāsuvihāro cā’ti."
msgstr ""
"‘Not for fun, indulgence, adornment, or decoration, but only to continue and "
"sustain this body, avoid harm, and support spiritual practice. So that I "
"will put an end to old discomfort and not give rise to new discomfort, and "
"so that I will keep on living blamelessly and at ease.’"

msgctxt "an8.9:3.4"
msgid "Idaṃ kho, bhikkhave, nandassa bhojane mattaññutāya hoti."
msgstr "This is how Nanda eats in moderation."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pli" id="pts-vp-pli4.168"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc4"></a>
msgctxt "an8.9:4.1"
msgid "Tatridaṃ, bhikkhave, nandassa jāgariyānuyogasmiṃ hoti."
msgstr "This is how Nanda is committed to wakefulness."

msgctxt "an8.9:4.2"
msgid ""
"Idha, bhikkhave, nando divasaṃ caṅkamena nisajjāya āvaraṇīyehi dhammehi "
"cittaṃ parisodheti;"
msgstr ""
"Nanda practices walking and sitting meditation by day, purifying his mind "
"from obstacles."

msgctxt "an8.9:4.3"
msgid ""
"rattiyā paṭhamaṃ yāmaṃ caṅkamena nisajjāya āvaraṇīyehi dhammehi cittaṃ "
"parisodheti;"
msgstr ""
"In the evening, he continues to practice walking and sitting meditation."

msgctxt "an8.9:4.4"
msgid ""
"rattiyā majjhimaṃ yāmaṃ dakkhiṇena passena sīhaseyyaṃ kappeti pāde pādaṃ "
"accādhāya sato sampajāno uṭṭhānasaññaṃ manasi karitvā;"
msgstr ""
"In the middle of the night, he lies down in the lion’s posture—on the right "
"side, placing one foot on top of the other—mindful and aware, and focused on "
"the time of getting up."

msgctxt "an8.9:4.5"
msgid ""
"rattiyā pacchimaṃ yāmaṃ paccuṭṭhāya caṅkamena nisajjāya āvaraṇīyehi dhammehi "
"cittaṃ parisodheti."
msgstr ""
"In the last part of the night, he gets up and continues to practice walking "
"and sitting meditation, purifying his mind from obstacles."

msgctxt "an8.9:4.6"
msgid "Idaṃ kho, bhikkhave, nandassa jāgariyānuyogasmiṃ hoti."
msgstr "This is how Nanda is committed to wakefulness."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc5"></a>
msgctxt "an8.9:5.1"
msgid "Tatridaṃ, bhikkhave, nandassa satisampajaññasmiṃ hoti."
msgstr "This is how Nanda has mindfulness and situational awareness."

msgctxt "an8.9:5.2"
msgid ""
"Idha, bhikkhave, nandassa viditā vedanā uppajjanti, viditā upaṭṭhahanti, "
"viditā abbhatthaṃ gacchanti;"
msgstr ""
"Nanda knows feelings as they arise, as they remain, and as they go away."

msgctxt "an8.9:5.3"
msgid "viditā saññā … pe …"
msgstr ""
"He knows perceptions as they arise, as they remain, and as they go away."

msgctxt "an8.9:5.4"
msgid "viditā vitakkā … pe … abbhatthaṃ gacchanti."
msgstr "He knows thoughts as they arise, as they remain, and as they go away."

msgctxt "an8.9:5.5"
msgid "Idaṃ kho, bhikkhave, nandassa satisampajaññasmiṃ hoti."
msgstr "This is how Nanda has mindfulness and situational awareness."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc6"></a>
msgctxt "an8.9:6.1"
msgid ""
"Kimaññatra, bhikkhave, nando indriyesu guttadvāro, bhojane mattaññū, "
"jāgariyaṃ anuyutto, satisampajaññena samannāgato, yehi nando sakkoti "
"paripuṇṇaṃ parisuddhaṃ brahmacariyaṃ caritun”ti."
msgstr ""
"How could Nanda live the full and pure spiritual life unless he guards the "
"sense doors, eats in moderation, is dedicated to wakefulness, and has "
"mindfulness and situational awareness?”"

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "an8.9:6.2"
msgid "Navamaṃ."
msgstr ""
